# PRs and issues are welcome
If you find a bug or an issue and feel like [reporting it](https://github.com/RewardedIvan/mcpvp-autogg/issues) or [even fixing it yourself](https://github.com/RewardedIvan/mcpvp-autogg/pulls), feel free to do so!  
I will try to fix and merge every issue/pr possible whenever I am free.
